<img src="http://biz-file.com/c/1805/440455.jpg" alt="The annual Amasa charity golf day 2018" width="444" height="628">The annual occasion will take place at the Randpark Golf Club on Friday, 1 June. The day is organised with the key aim to raise funds for the Amasa Bursary Fund to help uplift the education levels and expertise of the media industry. This is your chance to support the growth and development of our industry’s brightest young media talent... whilst enjoying a fun-filled day out in the Joburg sun. To add a hot twist of fun to the day, the event will be wrapped in a Mexican Fiesta theme and players will be encouraged to participate in the best-dressed competition. Date: Friday, 1 June 2018Registration: 08h30 – 09h30Shotgun start: 10h00Format: Four-Ball Alliance (2 scores to count)Awards dinner: 15h30 - 16h00 to 18h00 Venue: Randpark Golf Club, Firethorn Premium Course, Home of the Joburg Open, 2018 Best of Joburg 2016, www.randpark.co.za Sponsorship opportunities  ‘eStandar’ Four Ball - R7,150* / team of four 'Magnate’ Four Ball -                                    R8,000* / captain of industry Headline sponsor -                            R35,000* Hole Sponsors -                 R11,000 - R13,000* / hole Best dressed & photo booth -      R8,000*  *Excludes VAT. Terms and conditions apply. Be it a team build or your own special client invitation, you can build your own four-ball - R7,150*.Course fees, registration snacks, half-way lunch and early awards dinners Excludes: Caddie fees, golf cart, dress up, mulligans and out-of-package refreshments, etc. Contact Randpark Golf Club to book your caddies and golf carts in advance – first come, first serve.* Contacts Four-ball bookings - Tracey Chetty TraceyC@primedia.co.zabRev('brev-9d479eb2-b8d6-442e-904f-47822ebef0c9', '>a/\<az.oc.aidemirp@CyecarT>"az.oc.aidemirp;46#&CyecarT:otliam"=ferh a<')Sponsorships - Taryn Naledi Hood tarynh@primedia.co.zabRev('brev-13136ccf-1146-4dd4-bf87-0d38fc2ad2b1', '>a/\<az.oc.a